Implement fetch_models/1 for: - Ollama: GET http://{host}:{port}/api/tags, map models list. No auth needed. - Groq: GET https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/models with Bearer token. - OpenRouter: GET https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/models with Authorization header. Include context_length from OpenRouter's context_length field. Acceptance criteria: - Each provider returns {:ok, [model_info()]} on success - Ollama handles connection refused gracefully -> {:error, :unavailable} - OpenRouter context_length field populated from response - Groq supports_tools: true for llama-3 based models